about startalk leadership overview learning modules about startalk about cflp contact us about startalk startalk's mission is to increase the number of americans learning speaking and teaching critical need world languages by offering students k 16 and teachers of these languages creative and engaging learning experiences programs sponsored by startalk promote best practices in language education and teacher development forming a nationwide community of practice with the goal of supporting exemplary language and culture learning opportunities for all students additionally startalk conducts evaluation and research studies designed to enlighten the language teaching profession and inform policy in the area of language and culture education visit the startalk website to learn more
